data.name: AnchorOffsetCount.ToolTip
data.value:
The number of lines before or after a line from the file is anchored by the 'FilterKeep' expression. A negative value will go that many lines BEFORE the expression: -1 will go to 1st line right before the anchor, while -2 would be the second line before the anchored line.
Positive values will go that many lines AFTER the expression. 1 will be the line following the anchor.
